ActPublic Service Superannuation Act
PrecisAppointment of DEBORAH J. COOPER of Ottawa, Ontario, to be a member of the Public Service Pension Advisory Committee, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective September 7, 2021, in the place of Ron Cochrane, whose term will expire.
